{
  "stem": "6878.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a terrific speaker that used to absolutely-- it was just shiver the walls when he used to talk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN], he used to shout, [SPEAKING GERMAN] and this and that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was, obviously, started to be at bedtime for Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were invaded by the Russians in 1940, the Russian army, the propaganda of the Russians was terrific.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought that Russia will conquer the world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the army, we haven't seen any better armies, so we thought that that's a terrific army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the propaganda were terrific.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the Russians used to say, if any war, we'll win the war with trying capture the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'll win the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But fortunately, when the war started, Hitler had a terrific army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in a matter of three days, they invaded Lithuania, and not one of the Russian army soldiers and officers escaped from, from Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not one of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Most of them got slaughtered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first impression was that that's the end of our, our Jewish nation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, when we, we managed to run, that after two or three days running, on the way, the Germans used to come down with Messerschmitt, it used to call-- the plane-- over the heads of the people who were running and machine gun them.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- fortunately, we didn't-- we were in the same groups, but we used to low on the ground, fall to the ground, and they, they missed us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But a day later, they overrunned us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were 35 kilometers away from Kovna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, obviously, the trouble started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Big trouble started.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A month later, we were locked up in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That period of that month?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jewish were prosecuted straight away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was difficult for us to get out to any shops to get food.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
